Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:10.09,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}さぁ行け　みなみけ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:13.09,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}M-I-N-A-M-I-K-E
