Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:10.09,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}去吧  南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:13.09,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}M-I-N-A-M-I-K-E
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:18.22,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}单调的每一天  吹起一阵清风
